-- Ad Executive Signorelli Says ‘StoryBranding’ Works (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-05-30T21:58:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-30/ad-executive-signorelli-says-storybranding-works-audio-.html
     May 30 (Bloomberg) - Jim Signorelli, chief executive 
officer and chairman of ESW Partners/StoryLab, describes how he 
developed the effective concepts behind his work and new book, 
"StoryBranding: Creating Stand-Out Brands Through the Power of 
Story."  Signorelli, a 30-year veteran of the advertising 
industry, speaks with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie Quinn
on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 14:50
 